For An Act To Be Entitled
9 AN ACT TO AMEND THE LAW CONCERNING PUBLIC SAFETY
10 EMPLOYEES WHO HAVE EXPERIENCED A TRAUMATIC EVENT; TO
11 OFFER LICENSED COUNSELING TO PUBLIC SAFETY EMPLOYEES
12 WHO HAVE EXPERIENCED A TRAUMATIC EVENT; TO REQUIRE A
13 PUBLIC EMPLOYER TO PROVIDE COVERAGE FOR LICENSED
14 COUNSELING FOR A PUBLIC SAFETY EMPLOYEE WHO HAS
15 EXPERIENCED A TRAUMATIC EVENT; TO DECLARE AN
16 EMERGENCY; AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES.
