26 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
27
28 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 21, Chapter 5, Subchapter 1, is amended
29 to add an additional section to read as follows:
30 21-5-112. Coverage for licensed counseling for traumatic event —
31 Definitions.
32 (a) As used in this section:
33 (1) “Firefighter” means a person who is a:
34 (A) Paid, full-time member of a fire department or
35 firefighting unit of a public employer and who actively engages in the
36 fighting of fires on a regular basis;
